# Used by `npx flue dev --target cloudflare` (Worker B local dev). Copy to `.dev.vars`.
# Worker B is a pure model executor; its only runtime concerns are the model specifier
# (REASONING_MODEL in wrangler.jsonc) and provider API keys.
#
# Swapping providers is a one-secret + one-var change here, not a code change — see
# docs/adr/0001-flue-reasoning-worker.md. For OpenRouter, set OPENROUTER_API_KEY and
# change REASONING_MODEL to e.g. openrouter/openai/gpt-5.5.

OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key
